      <title>The effect of evergreen and deciduous trees on the organisms that live in and under them</title>
      <para id="id45391714"/>
      <section id="id45391719">
        <title>Activity: </title>
        <para id="para-id45391719">
<!--Empty sections are illegal in CNXML 0.5.  This empty paragraph is a place holder that was added as a byproduct of the word importer.-->
        </para>
